This is flagged as an open verification item. The structural argument — that 2001 is the year the deal changes, that Lucy acquires casting power, that a physical ringer for Kerri enters the public record as the McKenzie philosophical identity — is supported by the overall timeline and by the logic of the two-sisters thesis. The catalog credit is the documentary confirmation. It needs to be pulled.

